								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "One practical use of execution environments is controlling Epicea logging during tests. In {{gtMethod:EpMonitor>>#subscribeToSystemAnnouncer}}, code changes are only logged if:"
						},
						{
							"__type" : "textSnippet",
							"children" : {
								"__type" : "snippets",
